summary:
Moomin: Imagine the Moomin characters as Pokémon trainers.
Joxter: We both know what would happen.
Moomin & Joxter: Little My...
body:
Moomin: Imagine the Moomin characters as Pokémon trainers.

Joxter: We both know what would happen.

Moomin & Joxter: Little My would beat everyone up with a tiny but strong pokémon and Moominmamma would be the one to nurse them back to health, Moomintroll would be hugging his pokémon 24/7 and Moominpappa would brag about being formerly the Pokémon champion.

Moomin: Snufkin is the guy who tells you all the myths and stories that are going around. Joxter, Hodgkingson, Muddler and the Mymble are gym leaders, Joxter’s main pokémon is one lazy but highly intelligent snorlax.

Joxter: NOW WAIT A MINUTE-

summary: The Sniff Show (aka Moomin) episode 4 reactions
title: The Sniff Show (aka Moomin) episode 4 reactions
body:
- This is not the best song I ever heard Mr. Opening-Theme-Man

- BA BABA BA BA BA BABA BA BA!!!

- “The Moomins Discover the Island,” forever altering the native wildlife and ecosystem

- Just use the stairs, Moomin!

- See, Snork-Maiden agrees with me

- I thought Little My was just staying for the winter and was going to go home in episode 1. Why is she hanging around?

- Little My is gonna smack someone with that frying pan.

- Sniff would make an excellent captain

- That cargo is not properly secured. Is their food in there? Have they cleared customs?

- Sniff is justifiably concerned about the safe capacity of the boat

- Sniff generously offers to care for MoominHouse and smartly stays behind from the doomed expedition. 

- It’s impressive that Snufkin’s harmonica can generate an echo on the open sea.

- If they get stranded, eat Little My first

- Even if they don’t get stranded, eat Little My first

- DO NOT LISTEN TO THE SIREN SONG!

- Yes Hemulen, “rare plants” indeed. I’m sure Snufkin is after some “rare plants” as well.

- Who knows what endemic diseases await them within the forest?

- “White and ghostly and not very friendly looking.” Did Little My see her reflection?

- Well, Hemulen is a goner. 

- It’s like a mob of those floppy things you find in used-car dealerships

- Sniff would know what to do in this situation

- You had one job, Hemulen!

- Snufkin knows no fear

- Snufkin also seems to know everything

- That tent is bigger on the inside

- Awwwww. Moomin and S-Maiden are so cute.

- Cue ACDC’s Thunderstruck

- Oh shit they’re going super-saiyan

- The narrator does not inspire confidence

- Boat is gone. Eat Little My now.

-Stranded on a desert isl-WHIMSY!
